&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a senior individual contributor role for an executive recruiter who knows how to run a search — independently, rigorously, and to a high standard. Your primary focus will be identifying and closing Senior Sales Executives in the US market for Janea Systems, a premium software engineering consultancy whose clients include Fortune 500 companies. You will also take on other executive-level hires as they arise across the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a high-volume role. It is a high-judgement one. The Sales leaders Janea needs are a specific breed — enterprise hunters who can sell complex, bespoke engineering services into technical buyers. You will need to understand that profile deeply, build genuine relationships with passive candidates, and manage a search process that reflects the premium positioning of the company you represent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
