&lt;li&gt;Significant development experience with C#&amp;nbsp;and .NET.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building and deploying solutions on cloud services (Azure preferred)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp;designing, building, and&amp;nbsp;deploying&amp;nbsp;scalable, distributed applications using independent services, focusing on APIs, containers, cloud platforms (Azure&amp;nbsp;preferred), and CI/CD.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience contributing to AI/ML-enabled products, such as integrating ML models or AI services into production backend systems (e.g., APIs, pipelines, inference services).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience collaborating with ML/AI specialists&amp;nbsp;to translate models into scalable, reliable backend solutions (deployment, monitoring, performance, data flow).&lt;/li&gt;
